## Instructions

1. Set a timer for {{ time_limit_minutes }} minutes
2. Answer all {{ questions | length }} questions in order
3. Do not refer to study materials during the exam
4. Mark questions you are unsure about for review
5. After completing, check the [Answer Key](#answer-key) and review [Solutions](#solutions)

